---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import siteConfig from '@/site.config';

const pageTitle = "Getting Started with Web Accessibility - Sample Blog Post";
const pageDescription = "Learn the fundamentals of creating accessible websites that work for everyone.";
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <main class="blog-content">
    <!-- Blog Header -->
    <section class="blog-header">
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="/images/Placeholder.jpg" alt="Web accessibility illustration" />
      </div>

      <div class="blog-header-content">
        <div class="container">
          <!-- Category & Reading Time -->
          <div class="blog-meta-top">
            <span class="category-tag">Tutorial</span>
            <span class="featured-badge">Featured</span>
            <span class="reading-time">8 min read</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Title -->
          <h1 class="blog-title">Getting Started with Web Accessibility</h1>

          <!-- Description -->
          <p class="blog-description">Learn the fundamentals of creating accessible websites that work for everyone.</p>

          <!-- Author & Date -->
          <div class="blog-meta-bottom">
            <div class="author-info">
              <img src="/images/Placeholder.jpg" alt="Sarah Johnson" class="author-avatar" />
              <div class="author-details">
                <span class="author-name">Sarah Johnson</span>
                <time class="publish-date">March 15, 2024</time>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Blog Content -->
    <section class="blog-body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-grid">
          <article class="blog-article">
            <h2>Why Accessibility Matters</h2>
            <p>When we build accessible websites, we're opening our content to a much wider audience. Consider these statistics:</p>

            <ul>
              <li>Over 1 billion people worldwide have some form of disability</li>
              <li>15% of the world's population experiences some form of disability</li>
              <li>Many accessibility features benefit everyone, not just people with disabilities</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>The Four Principles of Accessibility</h2>
            <p>The Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) are built around four main principles. Content must be:</p>

            <h3>1. Perceivable</h3>
            <p>Information and user interface components must be presentable to users in ways they can perceive.</p>

            <h3>2. Operable</h3>
            <p>User interface components and navigation must be operable by all users.</p>

            <h3>3. Understandable</h3>
            <p>Information and the operation of user interface must be understandable.</p>

            <h3>4. Robust</h3>
            <p>Content must be robust enough that it can be interpreted reliably by a wide variety of user agents.</p>

            <blockquote>
              "Accessibility is not a feature you bolt on at the endâ€”it's a fundamental part of good web development."
            </blockquote>

            <h2>Getting Started: Quick Wins</h2>
            <p>Here are some simple things you can implement today to improve your site's accessibility:</p>

            <pre><code><!-- Good: Semantic structure -->
&lt;header&gt;
  &lt;nav&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="/about"&gt;About&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/nav&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;</code></pre>

            <p>Remember: accessibility benefits everyone. Start small, test often, and keep learning.</p>
          </article>

          <aside class="blog-sidebar">
            <!-- Tags -->
            <div class="sidebar-card">
              <h4>Tags</h4>
              <div class="tag-list">
                <span class="tag">Accessibility</span>
                <span class="tag">Web Design</span>
                <span class="tag">UX</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Share -->
            <div class="sidebar-card">
              <h4>Share This Post</h4>
              <div class="share-buttons">
                <a href="#" class="share-button twitter">
                  <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                  Twitter
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="share-button linkedin">
                  <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
                  LinkedIn
                </a>
                <button class="share-button copy">
                  <i class="fas fa-copy"></i>
                  Copy Link
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Back to Blog -->
            <div class="sidebar-card">
              <h4>More Articles</h4>
              <p>Explore more insights and articles.</p>
              <a href="/insights" class="cta-button">View All Posts</a>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .blog-content {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);
  }

  .blog-header {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    color: white;
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .hero-image {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .hero-image::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .blog-header-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .blog-meta-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .category-tag {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .featured-badge {
    background: var(--brand-accent-1);
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .reading-time {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .blog-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: white;
  }

  .blog-description {
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .blog-meta-bottom {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .author-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .author-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .author-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .publish-date {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .blog-body {
    padding: 4rem 0 667px;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .blog-article {
    max-width: none;
  }

  .blog-article h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 3rem 0 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .blog-article h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .blog-article p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .blog-article ul,
  .blog-article ol {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .blog-article li {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .blog-article blockquote {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 10%, transparent);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .blog-article pre {
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .blog-article code {
    font-family: 'Monaco', 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }

  /* Sidebar styles */
  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--color-background);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-secondary) 15%, transparent);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-secondary) 8%, transparent);
  }

  .sidebar-card h4 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .tag-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tag {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 10%, transparent);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 20%, transparent);
  }

  .share-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .share-button {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-secondary) 20%, transparent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: transparent;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .share-button:hover {
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-secondary) 5%, transparent);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Mobile responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .blog-header {
      padding: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .blog-body {
      padding: 2rem 0 667px;
    }

    .author-info {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .share-buttons {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .share-button {
      flex: 1;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 0;
    }
  }
</style>